               <h2 id="Recipe2">Beshbarmak</h2>
        
        <ul>
            <li>Time: 6 hours</li>
            <li>Serves: whole family </li>
        </ul>
        
        <table>
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Ingredients</th>
                    <th>Quantity</th>
                    <th>preparing time</th>
                </tr>
                
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                <td>water</td>
                <td>6L</td>
                <td> 6h </td>
                
             </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>meat</td>
                <td>1kg  </td>
                <td> 4h</td>
                
             </tr>

                <tr>
                <td>carrot</td>
                <td>100g </td>
                <td> 4h</td>
                
             </tr>
                          <tr>
                <td>onion</td>
                <td>250g </td>
                <td> 1h </td>
                
             </tr>

                          <tr>
                <td>potato</td>
                <td>500 g</td>
                <td> 1h </td>
                
             </tr>


                          <tr>
                <td>dough</td>
                <td>2kg</td>
                <td> 30 min </td>
                
             </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>
        
        <p><strong>Step 1:</strong>put meat into the water and cook it for 4 hours. 
</p>
        <p><strong>Step 2:</strong> add a carrot.
</p>
        <p><strong>Step3 :</strong>add carrot and onion into saucepan with meat and wait 4 hours.
</p>
        <p><strong>Step 4:</strong> add potato and reduce the fire. </p>
        <p><strong>Step 5:</strong> remove all previous ingridients and add dough, when you feel that it is ready. 
</p>

<img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/ru/thumb/e/e0/%D0%91%D0%B5%D1%88%D0%B1%D0%B0%D1%80%D0%BC%D0%B0%D0%BA.jpg/170px-%D0%91%D0%B5%D1%88%D0%B1%D0%B0%D1%80%D0%BC%D0%B0%D0%BA.jpg" alt ="error"> 
    <p><em>Source: <a href="https://gotovim-doma.ru/recipe/957-beshbarmak">Some recipes websites</a></em></p>
    
    

